w noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Private vaults in 1Password Teams and Business are now employee vaults | 1Password Blog</a><p class="mt-8 text-12 font-bold uppercase tracking-15 text-gray-63 dark:text-gray-bd">[<!-- -->1Password Blog<!-- -->]</p></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card group relative z-10 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-cc bg-white py-16 text-black last-of-type:border-b-0 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:border-gray-31 dark:bg-gray-13 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-md sm:pl-20 sm:pr-60 lg:py-40"><div class="flex items-center"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd relative z-10 mr-20 hidden md:block -rotate-180 border-l border-l-blurple pl-4 dark:border-l-franklin" style="writing-mode:vertical-lr;text-orientation:sideways"><a href="/streaming-wars">Streaming</a></span><div class="max-w-content-block-mobile sm:w-content-block-standard sm:max-w-content-block-standard"><div class="mb-6 flex md:hidden"><span class="duet--content-cards--content-card-group relative z-10 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-120 tracking-15 text-gray-4a dark:text-gray-bd border-b border-b-blurple pb-4 dark:border-b-franklin" style="writing-mode:initial;text-orientation:initial"><a href="/streaming-wars">Streaming</a></span></div><h2 class="font-polysans text-20 font-bold leading-100 tracking-1 md:text-24"><a class="after:absolute after:inset-0 group-hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:group-hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/2024/4/30/24145810/fubo-warner-bros-discovery-networks-streaming-drops">Fubo drops Discovery networks and blasts WBD for abusing its power</a></h2><div class="relative z-10 inline-block pt-4 font-polysans text-11 uppercase leading-140 tracking-15 text-gray-31 dark:text-gray-bd"><div class="inline-block"><a class="text-gray-31 hover:shadow-underline-inh